# IReport App Android

#[ 🚧 Work in progress 👷‍♀️⛏👷🔧️👷🔧 🚧 ] 

## Use case

Read and Report The local news.

## Java to kotlin migration in progress

The basic structure build old Android architecture to change new MVVM using kotlin language

## Code structure

The project uses Dagger 2 for DI, Rxjava2 for threading, Scarlet for Web socket connections and Some components of Architecture components

ViewModel is provided in the base Lifecycle owner class through generic and then bounded to the ViewModel factory

ViewModels depends on use cases where each task is handled through a Usecase